{"tid":1803593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃色經濟圈」- 道德撚既新天堂","createTime":"2019-12-30T10:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T14:52:27.000Z","uid":45123,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"14a183867c848977b149afa34d30866be7eb0622","tid":1803593,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"一直唔明點解話係黃色批鬥圈<br />\n<br />\n加入左個黃色經濟圈FB群即刻明點解<br />\n<br />\n唔播榮光又係藍<br />\n唔請/優惠啲學生又係藍<br />\n冇公開捐款又係藍<br />\n用少少大陸製物件又係藍<br />\n冇連儂牆又係藍<br />\n有錢賺就人血饅頭（不限於出名）<br />\n<br />\n要根正苗紅<br />\n最好就出晒位先可以係黃<br />\n<br />\n靠呢班黃色道德撚搞黃色經濟圈 死緊啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a2cf877c01acc6826ab47b45b0c41cb8954723","tid":1803593,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=d0cc47a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=6ce6915c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"c